query:
/*+ NoHashJoin(a1 q1 t1 tq1 u1) NoHashJoin(a1 acc q1 s t1 tq1 u1 b) */ select acc.location,
count(*)
from tag_question AS tq1
inner join question AS q1
on q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.score >= 0 AND q1.score <= 5
inner join tag AS t1
on t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND t1.name IN ('11.10',
'bluetooth',
'definition',
'exponential-function',
'fourier-series',
'graphics',
'keyboard',
'mount',
'network-manager',
'partitioning',
'predicate-logic',
'proof-explanation')
inner join answer AS a1
on q1.id = a1.question_id
inner join so_user AS u1
on a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND u1.upvotes >= 0 AND u1.upvotes <= 1
inner join account AS acc
on acc.id = u1.account_id
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = a1.site_id AND s.site_id = t1.site_id AND s.site_id = tq1.site_id AND s.site_id = u1.site_id AND s.site_id = q1.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('askubuntu',
'math')
inner join badge AS b
on s.site_id = b.site_id AND b.user_id = u1.id AND b.name IN ('Cleanup',
'Curious',
'Self-Learner') group by acc.location order by count(*) desc LIMIT 100;
